comments: whoa! beyond grand... i LOVE this!
Buddy could do the "ABC Song" and it would be great.

Looking at his work, you know that the legacy of the great musicians was transferred into the right hands. His expression in its purest form pleases because most musicians still trying to mix different styles.
The Blues scene now is international. In the '60s it was purely something that you would hear in black clubs, played by black musicians, especially in America. But from the '70s onwards it changed.
